title: The Coup Plotters and their Tech Titan Partners (Ep 1361)
description:
In this episode, I address the news about the President and coronavirus, along with the troubling liberal response. I also address the troubling links between the tech tyrants and the liberal coup plotters.

CNN sickos politicize the news about the President’s coronavirus infection.

Unpacking Joe Biden’s many lies about the Trump job creation miracle.

The economy continues to recover from the coronavirus scourge.
